# Financial Risk Capital Adequacy Future Claims Liability 50th Percentile Amount

## identifier
de14106

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the future claims liability, as defined in the Rules, that includes no risk margin to produce a 50% probability of adequacy.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.CapitalAdequacy.FutureClaimsLiability50thPercentile.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.25
- period=instant
